ilitation, painting instead a seemingly endless cycle of hunt, capture, and release.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aChurch work with drug addictszGuatemalazGuatemala. 0aDrug addictsxRehabilitationzGuatemalazGuatemala. 0aEvangelistic workzGuatemalazGuatemala. 0aInvoluntary treatmentzGuatemalazGuatemala. 0aPentecostalismxSocial aspectszGuatemalazGuatemala. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aGuatemala City.  aPentecostalism.  acaptivity.  apastoralism.  apredation.  arehabilitation.  asalvation.  asin.  awar on drugs.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311071194340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226624792423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226624792/original  a978-3-11-071194-3  University of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles